{"about_the_game":"A homage to the 90\u2019s horror movies and Series B slashers, FINAL GIRL is a bloodcurling turn based tactical in which your wits and survivability skills are the only things standing between you and a gruesome death.<br><br>Play through the different VHS, outsmart terrible foes, and piece together the story that links them all together!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669250/extras/finalGirl_steampage_titles_600x66_A.png?t=1732799527\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669250/extras/GIF1.gif?t=1732799527\" /><br>Play as a survivor of an 90's horror movie and use your ingenuity and your combativeness to to defy the odds and survive fearsome encounters. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669250/extras/finalGirl_steampage_titles_600x66_B.png?t=1732799527\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669250/extras/GIF2.gif?t=1732799527\" /><br>Use your environment, from a crowbar to a gas can, and confront creatures much stronger than you in turn-based fights. Explore small scaled but fully-packed tactical maps that\u2019ll get your blood pumping and your brain racking.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669250/extras/finalGirl_steampage_titles_600x66_C.png?t=1732799527\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669250/extras/GIF3.gif?t=1732799527\" /><br>Every time you play a new run, the enemy type, environment, interactable elements and objectives are randomized, keeping the strategy (and the spook!) fresh.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669250/extras/finalGirl_steampage_titles_600x66_D.p